item.title: Metrics
item.description: Friendly Name FQN Description Get Requests/sec Web_get_requests_per_sec The number of GET requests made per second. Post Requests/sec Web_post_requests_per_sec The number of POST requests made per second. Current Connections Web_current_connections The number of connections currently established with the web service. Connection Attempts/sec Web_connect_attempts_per_sec The number of connection attempts per second.
